To install the LSST schema browser:

1)
Create schema databases:
   mysql -e "CREATE DATABASE lsst_schema_browser_DC3a"
   mysql -e "CREATE DATABASE lsst_schema_browser_DC3b"


2)
Load the LSST schema metadata into mysql using command:

    mysql lsst_schema_browser_DC3a < metadata_DC3a.sql
    mysql lsst_schema_browser_DC3b < metadata_DC3b.sql


3)
Update DB_SERVER, DB_USER and DB_PASS in the file "constants.php"


4)
Put this whole directory in a place visible by the httpd server
eg, put a link to this directory from /var/www/html


